                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7345" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1147</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8949 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">票据管理路且长，区块技术解万难 ——S互联网企业区块链电子发票应用之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bill management road is long, block technology to solve all difficulties —— S Internet enterprise electronic bill management optimization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李永红，刘鑫鑫，赵红祥，段春晓，魏浩楠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">S互联网企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子票据；区块链；会计流程</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Electronic bills; Blockchain; Accounting process</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在数字技术快速更迭的时代背景下，会计电子票据可以帮助企业更好地管理企业经营和生产的工作，而针对会计电子票据的规范化管理成为了各大企业的焦点内容。区块链基于稳定的信息技术基础、算法、设备，建立起了全社会的信任架构，并且区块链并无统一的中心部署、可以溯源、不可逆的技术特点都很好地匹配了互联网业务操作的处理逻辑。区块链电子票据一经推出，便使得中国企业面临着机遇与挑战共同出现的局面；如何巧妙地将区块链技术与会计电子票据相结合，是目前 S 互联网企业及国内各大互联网公司急需关注的重点问题。案例首先阐述了电子票据管理在 S 互联网企业应用和运行中的困境，进而提出将区块链技术与会计电子票据管理融合，可以有效解决发票录入难、缺乏信任、数据真实性不足和信息孤岛等问题，从而提高互联网企业对于电子票据的广泛接受度，也为区块链技术的应用提供了充实的教学素材。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the era of rapid changes in digital technology, accounting electronic bills can help enterprises better manage their business and production, and standardized management of accounting electronic bills has become the focus of major enterprises. Based on a stable information technology foundation, algorithm, and equipment, the blockchain has established a trust architecture for the whole society, and the blockchain has no unified central deployment, traceable, and irreversible technical features that well match the processing logic of Internet business operations. Once the blockchain electronic bill was introduced, Chinese enterprises were faced with opportunities and challenges; How to skillfully combine blockchain technology with accounting electronic bills is a key issue that S Internet enterprises and domestic major Internet companies need to pay close attention to. The case first describes the difficulties of electronic bill management in the application and operation of S Internet enterprises, and then proposes that the integration of blockchain technology and accounting electronic bill management can effectively solve the problems of invoice entry difficulty, lack of trust, lack of data authenticity, and information islands, thus improving the wide acceptance of electronic bills by Internet enterprises, and also providing substantial teaching materials for the application of blockchain technology.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《区块链技术基础与实践》、《供应链金融》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子票据概念；区块链技术概念；区块链技术特征；“区块链+电子发票”应用；信息生命周期管理理论；沙盒监管；企业信息化建设风险理论；创新推广理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
